# React / JSX

- Functional components; default export for pages
- Feature UI under `src/components/<feature>/`
- `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for class merge
- Prefer `@/components/ui/*` primitives
- Colors via `var(--go-*)` — not `text-gray-*` / raw hex
- Workspace chrome = `Layout.jsx` only; marketing = `MarketingShell`

```jsx
// Prefer
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
<p style={{ color: "var(--go-text-secondary)" }}>…</p>

// Avoid
import Button from "../../components/ui/button"
<p className="text-gray-500">…</p>
```
